creator: karryapp
descriptionHtml:
In our application you will find a collection of the coolest and most interesting Wallpapers and Themes for your device on the Android operating system! Download the Jeffy Wallpaper, which we created specifically to decorate your favorite smartphone or tablet! Our application will allow you to set as the wallpaper the best and interesting pictures! You can enjoy popular and beautiful pictures every day and hour, always when you turn on your favorite device!
In our Wallpaper and Themes application you will find:
* The best, beautiful and specially selected HD, QHD, Full HD images!
* Very simple and convenient control, pictures can be set as wallpaper in one click!
* Optimize and support the most famous and popular in the world of tablets and smartphones: Microsoft, Xiaomi Mi Phone, One Plus, Lenovo, HTC, Samsung Galaxy, ASUS, LG G, Sony Xperia, Google Pixel, HTC, Motorola, Philips, Huawei, Nokia
* Save any image on the memory to the SD memory card or to the internal memory of the device!
* Send friends your favorite pictures via the worldwide Internet: email, dropbox, cloud, file sharing; Social networks and instant messengers: Facebook, VK, Line, Telegram, Line, Skype, WhatsApp, and any other way of sharing files over the Internet!
* If you have a personal computer running Windows, Ubuntu, MacOS you can use our pictures as wallpaper on them too! Just save the picture on the memory card, transfer it to a personal computer, and enjoy your favorite wallpaper in any available resolution!
* Specially for you the application is free, no in-game purchases !!!
Do not forget to leave your assessment and write a short review, this will help us create new interesting applications and exciting games! Be sure to check out our other apps and themes for your desktop wallpaper: 3D wallpapers and themes, Space and Galaxy, Butterflies and Insects, Clock and Time, Colors and Colors, Lovely Puppies and Beasts, Joy and Emotions, Gold and Jewels, Weapons and Armament , Christmas and New Year, Mountains and Nature, Music and Art, Sports and Hobby, Racing and Cars, Flowers and Plants, Snowfall and Winter, Super Heroes and Super Entertainment, Wolves and Predators ... enjoy !!!
